summary: An Ordinance transferring the sum of Eighteen and 21/100 Dollars ($18.21) from Local Improvement District No. 1949 Fund, into the General Fund on the City of Seattle, for the purpose of reimbursing said General Fund, for the deficiency in the Fixed Estimate of said district, for the improvement of West Roy Street et al, by constructing concrete sidewalks thereon, as provided for in Ordinance No. 20124.
